have the lambs stopped screaming?

1250
01:52:07,638 --> 01:52:08,805
Dr. Lecter.

1251
01:52:09,056 --> 01:52:11,975
Don't bother with a trace.
I won't be on long enough.

1252
01:52:15,646 --> 01:52:19,858
-Where are you, Dr. Lecter?
-I have no plans to call on you, Clarice.

1253
01:52:19,942 --> 01:52:22,444
The world's more interesting
with you in it.

1254
01:52:22,987 --> 01:52:26,156
So you take care now
to extend me the same courtesy.

1255
01:52:26,198 --> 01:52:28,658
You know I can't make that promise.

1256
01:52:29,201 --> 01:52:31,870
I do wish we could chat longer, but...

1257
01:52:32,914 --> 01:52:35,498
I'm having an old friend for dinner.

1258
01:52:37,043 --> 01:52:38,126
Bye.

1259
01:52:38,753 --> 01:52:40,170
Dr. Lecter...

1260
01:52:42,632 --> 01:52:44,007
Dr. Lecter.

1261
01:52:46,302 --> 01:52:47,677
Dr. Lecter.

1262
01:52:49,680 --> 01:52:51,014
Dr. Lecter.

1263
01:52:51,557 --> 01:52:53,683
Hey, what? Oh, excuse me. I'm sorry.

1264
01:52:54,018 --> 01:52:56,978
-Is the security system all set up?
-We have the big-shot security.

